{"data": [{"id": "4725286", "title": "Hancock Whitney: An Unfortunate Downgrade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Happy mid aged business woman manager handshaking greeting client in office.\" data-id=\"2004891062\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">insta_photos/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <p>One of my favorite things when it comes to investing is upgrading a company. However, one of my least favorite is downgrading one. I never want to see a company perform poorly. Rather, I would prefer that every business thrive. But that's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2004891062/image_2004891062.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725286-hancock-whitney-an-unfortunate-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-10-06 20:16:40"}, {"id": "4725285", "title": "O'Reilly Automotive Looks Vulnerable", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Apprentice engineer selecting tyres in car service centre\" data-id=\"1186093149\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <p>Auto parts retailers have been on a wild ride in 2024. Shares of the big players have soared and plummeted at various points, including <strong>O'Reilly Automotive</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORLY\" title=\"O'Reilly Automotive, Inc.\">ORLY</a></span>), which I consider to be certainly</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186093149/image_1186093149.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725285-oreilly-auto-looks-vulnerable", "pub_date": "2024-10-06 20:13:02"}, {"id": "4725283", "title": "Vinci: Deleveraging Somewhat Slowed By New Taxes", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Long straight road in desert landscape\" data-id=\"1857365586\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1019px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Gary Yeowell/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <p><strong>Vinci</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VCISF\" title=\"Vinci SA\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:VCISF</a>)(<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VCISY\" title=\"Vinci SA\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:VCISY</a>) remains a deleveraging play as we pointed out in our <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4684249-vinci-deleveraging-nicely-on-top-of-its-4-percent-dividend-yield\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4684249-vinci-deleveraging-nicely-on-top-of-its-4-percent-dividend-yield\" target=\"_blank\">previous article</a>, but the equity case hasn't been helped by the new taxes that have been passed into</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1857365586/image_1857365586.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725283-vinci-deleveraging-somewhat-slowed-by-new-taxes", "pub_date": "2024-10-06 19:38:53"}, {"id": "4725281", "title": "A More Bullish Sentiment Could Push Baidu Much Higher", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Baidu Headquarters\" data-id=\"458699011\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3504px\" height=\"2336px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">V2images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4674744-baidu-ai-profiteer-positioned-for-long-term-growth\">My last article </a>about Baidu, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BIDU\" title=\"Baidu, Inc.\">BIDU</a></span>) was published about seven months ago on February 29, 2024, and similar to my other articles about Baidu I have written in the last few years, I was bullish once again. And since my</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458699011/image_458699011.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725281-a-more-bullish-sentiment-could-push-baidu-much-higher", "pub_date": "2024-10-06 19:30:00"}, {"id": "4725282", "title": "IWL: The Biggest Of The Big", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Boy with teddy prize\" data-id=\"1539766989\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Tara Moore/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <p>The stock market is really, at this point, just a collection of very large companies driving headline averages. This has not been a kind cycle to small-caps. Candidly, I'm doubtful large-cap momentum continues, but I've been wrong clearly in sounding the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1539766989/image_1539766989.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725282-iwl-the-biggest-of-the-big", "pub_date": "2024-10-06 19:21:23"}, {"id": "4725279", "title": "Spotify: Why AI Accelerates Their Business", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Spotify Raises Its Monthly Price For 2nd Year In A Year\" data-id=\"2156022065\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Michael M. Santiago/Getty Images News</p></figcaption></figure></p> <p>Co-Authored By Noah Cox and Brock Heilig.</p> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Since I last wrote about Spotify (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPOT\" title=\"Spotify Technology S.A.\">SPOT</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4698035-spotify-price-hike-bullish\">over the summer</a>, shares are up over 20%, driven by strong operating performance driven (in part) by the price</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156022065/image_2156022065.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725279-spotify-why-ai-accelerate-their-business", "pub_date": "2024-10-06 19:15:00"}, {"id": "4725255", "title": "AMD: Overvalued In The Shadow Of Nvidia", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Advertising banner on the facade of the stadium\" data-id=\"1369211203\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"786px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Pavel Byrkin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <h2>Investment thesis</h2> <p>My <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4705695-amd-valuation-concerns-persist-despite-recent-dip\">previous bearish thesis</a> about AMD's stock (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMD\" title=\"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.\">AMD</a></span>) might seem mistaken as the stock has gained 5% since July. On the other hand, it is common when short-term price movements do not align with fundamental developments.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369211203/image_1369211203.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725255-amd-overvalued-in-the-shadow-of-nvidia", "pub_date": "2024-10-06 19:00:00"}, {"id": "4725229", "title": "Is Enbridge S